{
  "stem": "15938.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he came to Auschwitz, I think roundabout August.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think I saw him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it would have been my imagination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't prove that I saw him there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because somebody send me a message.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Come.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You're father is here, you know near in the barrack, where they collected to go to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I looked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I thought I saw him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But either I didn't want to see him, because I knew where he was going, or maybe it wasn't him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I was told it was him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I stayed there till January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's what I was doing all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had our ration, a bowl of food-- a bowl of-- call it muck, whatever, soup, and a cup of coffee, black coffee, and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I must say that sometimes we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when we were sorting the clothes, in some pockets we sometimes found a little bit of bread or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's why it's Kanada, because Kanada was described as the rich land.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So our company was called Kanada.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because there was rich picking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean if you found peace of bread, it was rich picking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also the diamonds and the jewelry, what went through our hands was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And our aim was never to give it to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So whenever if we found them, either we flushed them down the toilet or dug them somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the men used to come from another barrack, another camp to collect the stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we managed to kind of give it to them that they should either dispose of it, we couldn't do anything with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Diamonds, I can't tell you the amount of diamonds and gold and jewelry which was hidden.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
